---
import Badge from "./Badge.astro";
import Button from "./Button.astro";
---

<header class="text-center w-[300px] sm:w-[700px]">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
    <h1 class="text-lime-500 text-4xl sm:text-7xl font-bold">Jakub Dorničák</h1>
    <Badge
      text="Fullstack Web developer, Cybersecurity enthusiast & Aspiring sys-admin"
    />
    <p class="text-gray-500 table w-fit mx-auto text-justify">
      I am an <b>18 year old student and technology enthusiast</b>. I have built
      my knowledge and skills primarily in the field of

      <b>Web development</b> where I have been developing for several years websites
      and applications for all kinds of Eshops and freelancers. Outside of web development,
      I have been working on UNIX systems and their administration ⚙️,

      <b>Cybersecurity</b> (HackTheBox, TryHackMe challenges) and also some networking.
      My interests outside of IT mainly include my dog 🐕 and learning DJ'ing 🎉.
    </p>

    <div>
      <h3>Available on:</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-row gap-2 mx-auto w-fit">
        <Button
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jakub-dorni%C4%8D%C3%A1k-b6953423b/"
          icon="mdi:linkedin"
          iconOnly
        >
          Linkedin
        </Button>
        <Button iconOnly href="https://github.com/Atsukoro1" icon="mdi:github">
          Github
        </Button>
        <Button
          href="https://app.hackthebox.com/users/692313"
          icon="simple-icons:hackthebox"
          iconOnly
        >
          HackTheBox
        </Button>
        <Button
          iconOnly
          href="mailto:dornicakkuba@gmail.com"
          icon="simple-icons:gmail"
        >
          Gmail
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
